# Ignore Agent OS Specs

- Do not add or commit files under `agent-os/specs/`.
- Keep `agent-os/specs/` covered by `.gitignore`.
- If files under `agent-os/specs/` are already tracked, remove them from the index with `git rm --cached` before updating the branch.
